graph LR
    subgraph Topology["Local / Single-Node Cluster Topology"]
        Client["YARN Client (Host)"] -->|Submit Jobs| RM["ResourceManager Container (Port 8088/8032)"]
        RM -->|Task Assignment| NM["NodeManager Container"]
        NM -->|Mount Socket| HostDocker["Host Docker Daemon"]
        HostDocker -->|Launches Sibling Container| Workload["Workload Container"]
    end
